<h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2 leading-tight">Counting Tiles Strategy</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8 not-prose">Quiz · Dictionary</p>


      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">
        <time datetime="2026-06-15">June 15, 2026</time>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>7 min read</span>
      </div>

      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
        Every competitive Scrabble player has a secret weapon that doesn't require memorising obscure words — it's knowing exactly what's left. Tile counting transforms Scrabble from a vocabulary game into a game of deduction, letting you predict your opponent's options and dominate the endgame with perfect information.
      </p>

      <!-- Section 1 -->
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">What Is Tile Counting?</h2>

      <p>Tile counting (or tile tracking) is the practice of monitoring which letters have been played during a game. Since Scrabble uses a fixed set of 100 tiles with a known distribution, every tile placed on the board is information you can use. By tracking what's gone, you deduce what remains — in the bag, and eventually on your opponent's rack.</p>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-4 rounded-r-lg my-6">
        <p class="font-semibold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300 mb-1">💡 Key Insight</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-200">You always know 7 tiles (your rack) + all tiles on the board. The unknowns shrink with every turn. By endgame, you can know your opponent's exact rack.</p>
      </div>

      <p>This isn't cheating — it's a fundamental skill taught in every competitive Scrabble training programme. The tile bag contents are public information (printed on every box), and tracking what's been played is simply paying attention.</p>

      <!-- Section 2 -->
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">The Complete Scrabble Tile Distribution</h2>

      <p>A standard English Scrabble set contains exactly 100 tiles. Knowing this distribution by heart is the foundation of tile tracking:</p>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto my-6">
        <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg">
          <thead class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800">
            <tr>
              <th class="px-3 py-2 text-left">Tile</th>
              <th class="px-3 py-2 text-center">Count</th>
              <th class="px-3 py-2 text-center">Points</th>
              <th class="px-3 py-2 text-left">Tile</th>
              <th class="px-3 py-2 text-center">Count</th>
              <th class="px-3 py-2 text-center">Points</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200 dark:divide-gray-700">
            <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">A</td><td class="text-center">9</td><td class="text-center">1</td><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">N</td><td class="text-center">6</td><td class="text-center">1</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">B</td><td class="text-center">2</td><td class="text-center">3</td><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">O</td><td class="text-center">8</td><td class="text-center">1</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">C</td><td class="text-center">2</td><td class="text-center">3</td><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">P</td><td class="text-center">2</td><td class="text-center">3</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">D</td><td class="text-center">4</td><td class="text-center">2</td><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">Q</td><td class="text-center">1</td><td class="text-center">10</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">E</td><td class="text-center">12</td><td class="text-center">1</td><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">R</td><td class="text-center">6</td><td class="text-center">1</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">F</td><td class="text-center">2</td><td class="text-center">4</td><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">S</td><td class="text-center">4</td><td class="text-center">1</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">G</td><td class="text-center">3</td><td class="text-center">2</td><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">T</td><td class="text-center">6</td><td class="text-center">1</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">H</td><td class="text-center">2</td><td class="text-center">4</td><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">U</td><td class="text-center">4</td><td class="text-center">1</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">I</td><td class="text-center">9</td><td class="text-center">1</td><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">V</td><td class="text-center">2</td><td class="text-center">4</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">J</td><td class="text-center">1</td><td class="text-center">8</td><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">W</td><td class="text-center">2</td><td class="text-center">4</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">K</td><td class="text-center">1</td><td class="text-center">5</td><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">X</td><td class="text-center">1</td><td class="text-center">8</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">L</td><td class="text-center">4</td><td class="text-center">1</td><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">Y</td><td class="text-center">2</td><td class="text-center">4</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">M</td><td class="text-center">2</td><td class="text-center">3</td><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono">Z</td><td class="text-center">1</td><td class="text-center">10</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 font-mono" colspan="3">Blank: 2 tiles (0 points)</td><td colspan="3" class="px-3 py-1 font-bold">Total: 100 tiles</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 my-4">
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/40 text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-300 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">12 × E</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/40 text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-300 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">9 × A</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/40 text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-300 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">9 × I</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/40 text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-300 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">8 × O</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/40 text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-300 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">6 × N, R, T</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/40 text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-300 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">1 × J, K, Q, X, Z</span>
